WEBVTT

00:00.472 --> 00:04.674
Hyundai is planning a new electric vehicle manufacturing plant in the U.S....

00:04.933 --> 00:07.709
...with discussions about building a facility in Georgia...

00:07.885 --> 00:10.584
...near the South Korean automaker's existing plants.

00:11.437 --> 00:13.856
Hyundai confirmed it would announce a plan soon.

00:14.706 --> 00:19.192
The Biden administration has been pushing for more investments in EV production...

00:19.483 --> 00:23.399
...and related suppliers to create jobs and drive a clean energy agenda.

00:23.716 --> 00:28.153
It says it will allocate more than 3 billion dollars in infrastructure funding...

00:28.350 --> 00:30.789
...to help make good on its pledge for half of the vehicles...

00:30.924 --> 00:33.918
...sold in the United States to be electric by 2030.

00:34.470 --> 00:38.301
In April, Hyundai announced a 300-million-dollar investment...

00:38.501 --> 00:42.721
...to manufacture all electric and hybrid vehicles at its Alabama plant.

